   "source": [
    "13. What can you do to save a programme from crashing if it encounters an error?\n",
    "\n",
    "Exception handling\n",
    "try and except statements\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "14. What is the purpose of the try clause? What is the purpose of the except clause?\n",
    "\n",
    "Statements that can raise an error/Suspicious code is kept inside try block\n",
    "\n",
    "Statements that can handle the error are written inside except clause."
   ]
